1
00:01:24,870 --> 00:01:26,760
Lu Fan, why are you here?

2
00:01:26,950 --> 00:01:27,590
What...

3
00:01:30,680 --> 00:01:31,740
What are you doing?

4
00:01:36,640 --> 00:01:37,500
Where is Su Xia?

5
00:01:37,509 --> 00:01:38,479
She's not here.

6
00:01:39,479 --> 00:01:41,039
Where is she? Tell me.

7
00:01:41,070 --> 00:01:42,400
She went to the clinic.

8
00:01:42,840 --> 00:01:43,479
Lu Fan.

9
00:01:45,070 --> 00:01:47,130
You know about Xiao Qi's plan, right?

10
00:01:59,430 --> 00:02:00,870
So you all knew?

11
00:02:02,950 --> 00:02:04,120
Only I, Lu Fan,

12
00:02:04,120 --> 00:02:05,680
like a clown,

13
00:02:05,950 --> 00:02:07,280
was played by all of you.

14
00:02:09,470 --> 00:02:10,750
Right, I forgot.

15
00:02:11,750 --> 00:02:13,630
This is your Su family's skill,

16
00:02:13,910 --> 00:02:17,400
enduring 10 years in an enemy's home for revenge.

17
00:02:19,750 --> 00:02:21,150
What a great act.

18
00:02:22,840 --> 00:02:24,840
Such scheme and patience—

19
00:02:25,590 --> 00:02:27,120
I, Lu Fan, concede defeat.

20
00:02:27,120 --> 00:02:27,870
Lu Fan.

21
00:02:28,840 --> 00:02:30,170
It's not what you think.

22
00:02:30,430 --> 00:02:32,590
Su Xia is sincere with you.

23
00:02:34,470 --> 00:02:36,329
She's been controlled by Xiao Qi.

24
00:02:37,079 --> 00:02:38,430
She's a victim too.

25
00:02:39,190 --> 00:02:40,079
For you,

26
00:02:40,470 --> 00:02:41,800
she betrayed Xiao Qi.

27
00:02:42,000 --> 00:02:43,400
If she wanted to harm you,

28
00:02:43,590 --> 00:02:45,250
why would she come back to you?

29
00:02:46,240 --> 00:02:47,750
And after you disappeared, she wouldn't have

30
00:02:47,750 --> 00:02:49,880
looked everywhere for you like crazy,

31
00:02:50,360 --> 00:02:51,560
let alone

32
00:02:51,710 --> 00:02:53,960
risked her life to save you.

33
00:02:56,590 --> 00:02:58,000
Lu Fan, trust me.

34
00:02:58,840 --> 00:03:02,360
The grudge between the Su and Lu families has long been settled.

35
00:03:02,360 --> 00:03:04,160
Xia's feelings for you are real.

36
00:03:24,750 --> 00:03:25,680
Why are you here?

37
00:03:35,310 --> 00:03:36,030
You...

38
00:04:03,190 --> 00:04:04,390
What happened to you?

39
00:05:10,630 --> 00:05:11,310
Dad.

40
00:05:12,480 --> 00:05:14,680
Good and evil eventually get their due.

41
00:05:14,750 --> 00:05:17,280
The consequences of what you sowed back then—

42
00:05:17,630 --> 00:05:19,270
the Su family, the Tang family,

43
00:05:19,270 --> 00:05:22,470
and the debts owed by those whose families you destroyed—

44
00:05:22,800 --> 00:05:24,460
I have repaid them all for you.

45
00:05:27,040 --> 00:05:28,900
With the dignity of the Lu family,

46
00:05:29,070 --> 00:05:30,200
with my own dignity.

47
00:05:31,750 --> 00:05:34,070
And it almost cost my life.

48
00:05:35,800 --> 00:05:37,120
You struggled, fought,

49
00:05:37,120 --> 00:05:38,720
and exhausted every scheme,

50
00:05:39,000 --> 00:05:41,000
but it was all for nothing in the end.

51
00:05:41,430 --> 00:05:42,630
The Lu family is gone.

52
00:05:43,310 --> 00:05:45,159
I couldn't save it in the end.

53
00:05:52,390 --> 00:05:54,680
Dad, Su Xia and I

54
00:05:55,920 --> 00:05:57,390
are getting married soon.

55
00:06:00,720 --> 00:06:02,920
This is the last time I'm here to see you.

56
00:06:03,040 --> 00:06:04,120
I don't want

57
00:06:04,630 --> 00:06:06,960
her to have any bad memories
in the future.

58
00:06:07,950 --> 00:06:09,720
If we have a child in the future,

59
00:06:14,920 --> 00:06:16,650
during the Tomb-Sweeping Day,

60
00:06:17,950 --> 00:06:19,210
we will pay you a visit.

61
00:06:45,270 --> 00:06:47,390
Xi, what are you thinking about?

62
00:06:52,510 --> 00:06:54,800
Yesterday,
while playing golf with Mr. Meng,

63
00:06:54,800 --> 00:06:58,060
he proposed a marriage alliance
between our two families.

64
00:06:58,680 --> 00:07:00,870
They have a son named Meng Yan.

65
00:07:01,310 --> 00:07:03,110
His age is a good match for yours.

66
00:07:05,120 --> 00:07:06,920
He is a very handsome young man.

67
00:07:11,070 --> 00:07:12,390
I'll arrange it in the next few days

68
00:07:12,390 --> 00:07:13,600
so you can meet, okay?

69
00:07:14,310 --> 00:07:16,310
As for the place, let's choose Yunding.

70
00:07:16,310 --> 00:07:17,560
The environment is nice,

71
00:07:17,560 --> 00:07:18,820
and it's very private.

72
00:07:22,120 --> 00:07:24,070
You need to prepare well.

73
00:07:26,480 --> 00:07:27,510
Let me tell you,

74
00:07:28,870 --> 00:07:30,270
with the Meng family's

75
00:07:30,270 --> 00:07:32,870
connections and resources
in Southeast Asia,

76
00:07:33,270 --> 00:07:35,040
if we can connect with them,

77
00:07:36,720 --> 00:07:39,600
then the future development
of our Jian Group...

78
00:07:42,070 --> 00:07:42,680
Dad,

79
00:07:43,920 --> 00:07:45,720
I want to go abroad for a while.

80
00:07:49,510 --> 00:07:50,310
Go abroad?

81
00:07:51,159 --> 00:07:51,950
Now?

82
00:07:54,480 --> 00:07:55,680
Are you kidding?

83
00:07:56,270 --> 00:07:57,600
Now is the crucial time for the Jian Group

84
00:07:57,600 --> 00:07:59,560
to ride the wave of momentum.

85
00:08:01,190 --> 00:08:02,750
Do you know how many pairs of eyes

86
00:08:02,750 --> 00:08:03,680
are watching us?

87
00:08:04,720 --> 00:08:07,650
And how many specific things
need your supervision?

88
00:08:07,680 --> 00:08:09,070
At this time, instead of staying in the country

89
00:08:09,070 --> 00:08:10,950
to help me stabilize the situation
and expand the business,

90
00:08:10,950 --> 00:08:13,750
you actually going abroad?
What are you thinking?

91
00:08:14,240 --> 00:08:15,640
You are not allowed to go.

92
00:08:15,720 --> 00:08:17,160
I have made up my mind.

93
00:08:26,040 --> 00:08:26,900
How about this?

94
00:08:26,950 --> 00:08:29,210
The most urgent thing is to meet Meng Yan.

95
00:08:29,270 --> 00:08:30,270
Tomorrow night.

96
00:08:30,390 --> 00:08:33,590
Tomorrow night, I'll send a driver
to take you to Yunding.

97
00:08:35,720 --> 00:08:36,360
Dad,

98
00:08:37,750 --> 00:08:39,549
am I your biological daughter?

99
00:08:40,120 --> 00:08:42,789
What nonsense are you talking about?

100
00:08:43,840 --> 00:08:45,040
Forget it. I'm tired.

101
00:08:45,320 --> 00:08:46,780
I'm going upstairs first.

102
00:08:54,870 --> 00:08:55,630
Mr. Xiao,

103
00:08:56,030 --> 00:08:58,200
I came here specifically to thank you.

104
00:08:59,150 --> 00:08:59,840
Thank me?

105
00:09:00,360 --> 00:09:02,240
For keeping my word, or for...

106
00:09:02,320 --> 00:09:04,910
helping the Jian family
completely swallow up

107
00:09:04,910 --> 00:09:06,840
the Lu family's last prized asset?

108
00:09:07,630 --> 00:09:08,390
Both.

109
00:09:10,480 --> 00:09:13,880
You have fulfilled everything
you promised the Jian family.

110
00:09:14,440 --> 00:09:17,790
The Lu family's last batch
of core resources and channels

111
00:09:18,550 --> 00:09:20,960
were successfully integrated
by the Jian family,

112
00:09:20,960 --> 00:09:22,690
which saved us a lot of trouble.

113
00:09:23,030 --> 00:09:23,750
So,

114
00:09:24,960 --> 00:09:25,600
thank you.

115
00:09:29,750 --> 00:09:30,480
And then?

116
00:09:31,750 --> 00:09:32,390
I'm...

117
00:09:33,840 --> 00:09:35,150
leaving this place.

118
00:09:35,790 --> 00:09:38,240
I've been in this place of trouble
for too long.

119
00:09:38,240 --> 00:09:39,000
I'm tired.

120
00:09:39,910 --> 00:09:40,750
The Jian family is

121
00:09:40,750 --> 00:09:42,360
at its peak right now.

122
00:09:42,870 --> 00:09:43,790
Not pressing your advantage

123
00:09:43,790 --> 00:09:45,510
to completely crush the Lu family?

124
00:09:45,510 --> 00:09:46,840
That's not your style.

125
00:09:48,390 --> 00:09:49,600
If you let go now,

126
00:09:50,030 --> 00:09:52,290
Lu Fan is not someone who gives up easily.

127
00:09:53,360 --> 00:09:54,870
What if he makes a comeback one day?

128
00:09:54,870 --> 00:09:55,630
Mr. Xiao.

129
00:09:56,360 --> 00:09:57,720
Business is business.

130
00:09:58,870 --> 00:10:00,870
We got what we came for.

131
00:10:01,320 --> 00:10:02,600
Going for the kill...

132
00:10:03,150 --> 00:10:04,320
is not necessary.

133
00:10:05,120 --> 00:10:05,910
Besides,

134
00:10:06,960 --> 00:10:10,200
Lu Fan and I have been together
for over 10 years.

135
00:10:11,320 --> 00:10:12,870
Although it ended badly,

136
00:10:14,960 --> 00:10:18,120
it wasn't all just
fake feelings and calculation.

137
00:10:19,270 --> 00:10:21,600
I don't really want to see him
at a dead end.

138
00:10:22,150 --> 00:10:23,950
You're very generous, Ms. Jian.

139
00:10:24,870 --> 00:10:26,390
It seems these 10 years

140
00:10:26,390 --> 00:10:28,480
have softened your heart after all.

141
00:10:33,510 --> 00:10:35,840
When you heard they were getting married,

142
00:10:36,600 --> 00:10:38,600
weren't you a little jealous

143
00:10:39,600 --> 00:10:40,400
or resentful?

144
00:10:41,320 --> 00:10:42,840
Didn't you feel anything?

145
00:10:45,270 --> 00:10:46,320
It seems you

146
00:10:46,320 --> 00:10:48,780
already know
that they are getting married.

147
00:10:50,030 --> 00:10:50,840
I think

148
00:10:52,150 --> 00:10:55,080
the one who should be jealous
and resentful isn't me.

149
00:10:55,790 --> 00:10:56,870
I wish them well.

150
00:11:00,320 --> 00:11:01,720
What about you, Mr. Xiao?

151
00:11:07,030 --> 00:11:07,910
Mr. Xiao,

152
00:11:08,510 --> 00:11:09,240
goodbye.

153
00:11:53,390 --> 00:11:54,030
Dad.

154
00:11:56,320 --> 00:11:57,600
I've decided to

155
00:11:58,320 --> 00:12:00,000
bury you and Mom together.

156
00:12:00,840 --> 00:12:02,700
She waited for you her whole life,

157
00:12:03,480 --> 00:12:06,480
hated you her whole life,
and loved you her whole life.

158
00:12:08,550 --> 00:12:09,270
Down there,

159
00:12:10,840 --> 00:12:12,500
you can settle it yourselves.

160
00:12:15,270 --> 00:12:16,080
As for you,

161
00:12:17,790 --> 00:12:19,270
I hope in your next life

162
00:12:20,510 --> 00:12:21,840
you'll be a good person.

163
00:12:31,150 --> 00:12:31,960
You're here?

164
00:12:32,390 --> 00:12:33,360
Just visiting.

165
00:12:34,320 --> 00:12:37,120
And bringing you some news.

166
00:12:39,480 --> 00:12:40,200
News?

167
00:12:41,720 --> 00:12:43,120
What news could there be?

168
00:12:44,200 --> 00:12:45,480
Is it about him?

169
00:12:45,960 --> 00:12:47,120
Or about those debts?

170
00:12:47,120 --> 00:12:48,080
It's about you.

171
00:12:50,550 --> 00:12:52,960
Before your father Lu Zhen'an left,

172
00:12:52,960 --> 00:12:54,790
he actually held something back.

173
00:12:54,790 --> 00:12:56,360
He set up an overseas

174
00:12:56,360 --> 00:12:57,790
family trust fund.

175
00:12:58,960 --> 00:13:00,360
It's highly confidential,

176
00:13:00,360 --> 00:13:03,030
bypassing all debts and known procedures.

177
00:13:04,440 --> 00:13:06,030
You are the beneficiary, Fan.

178
00:13:06,030 --> 00:13:07,360
You are the sole heir.

179
00:13:08,960 --> 00:13:09,480
A fund?

180
00:13:11,030 --> 00:13:11,750
For me?

181
00:13:14,270 --> 00:13:16,120
Are you sure there's no mistake?

182
00:13:16,240 --> 00:13:17,840
The lawyer has reviewed it.

183
00:13:17,840 --> 00:13:19,320
All procedures are complete.

184
00:13:19,320 --> 00:13:20,360
And Fan,

185
00:13:21,630 --> 00:13:22,960
the amount in it

186
00:13:25,000 --> 00:13:27,000
is enough for you to make a comeback.

187
00:13:40,790 --> 00:13:41,630
Lu Zhen'an,

188
00:13:43,200 --> 00:13:45,060
you really are very calculating.

189
00:13:46,200 --> 00:13:48,860
Even after death, you use money to prove you won,

190
00:13:48,910 --> 00:13:51,240
to prove the Lu family always has a way out,

191
00:13:51,510 --> 00:13:54,710
and to prove you're still Mr. Lu
who controls everything.

192
00:13:55,080 --> 00:13:55,750
Right?

193
00:13:57,360 --> 00:13:59,960
You use blood-stained money
to compensate me.

194
00:14:02,080 --> 00:14:04,510
Do you want me
to keep living in your shadow?

195
00:14:06,270 --> 00:14:07,870
Make a comeback?

196
00:14:11,720 --> 00:14:12,670
Forget it.

197
00:14:17,240 --> 00:14:19,630
I want to have the wedding with Su Xia as soon as possible.
